spec_data.Name: python2-troveclient
spec_data.Description:
This is a client for the Trove API. There's a Python API (the
troveclient module), and a command-line script (trove). Each
implements 100% (or less ;) ) of the Trove API.

spec_data.Summary: Client library for OpenStack DBaaS API
